Log:
  Add more files to orphans white list:
  - .DS_Store files
  - some VCS related files

  Note: it's still recommended to not extract/install those files if they are
  not needed

  PR:		ports/189859
  Submitted by:	adamw (first version)
  Reviewed by:	bapt
  With hat:	portmgr

